WEBVTT

01:37.930 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:43.990
[Episode 7]

02:14.470 --> 02:15.120
It's fine.

02:15.210 --> 02:16.010
No one is here.

02:20.530 --> 02:22.270
Are you here to laugh at me?

02:24.240 --> 02:24.870
Yes.

02:25.290 --> 02:26.620
I came up to laugh at you.

02:26.770 --> 02:27.410
Keep doing it.

02:27.410 --> 02:29.270
I'm not in the mood for your jokes.

02:31.860 --> 02:33.660
You shouldn't be called Xu Miyu,

02:33.750 --> 02:35.750
but Xu Eyu, which means harsh words.

02:36.030 --> 02:37.870
Xu Miyu wasn't my real name.

02:39.310 --> 02:40.560
My stepsister's name

02:40.560 --> 02:41.690
has the word Mi in it.

02:42.829 --> 02:44.290
So, my mom changed my name.

02:44.560 --> 02:46.910
She said sisters should match.

02:47.300 --> 02:50.160
Actually, she just wanted
to please my stepfather.

02:51.190 --> 02:52.120
Then, I've been

02:52.370 --> 02:53.630
called Xu Miyu

02:53.630 --> 02:54.750
for over 20 years,

02:55.590 --> 02:58.350
flattering them with sweet words
for over 20 years.

02:58.350 --> 03:01.150
I thought sincerity could finally
win sincerity,

03:01.180 --> 03:02.280
but I didn't expect

03:04.710 --> 03:06.640
to fail miserably in the end.

03:07.010 --> 03:07.870
I'm like a joke.

03:10.110 --> 03:12.970
Have you ever heard of a bird
called Barnacle Goose?

03:15.020 --> 03:17.020
They live in the Arctic Circle.

03:17.880 --> 03:19.170
To avoid predators,

03:19.630 --> 03:21.750
they all build their nests on cliffs.

03:22.750 --> 03:24.350
But there is no food up there.

03:24.750 --> 03:26.840
The fledglings that haven't learned
to fly yet

03:26.840 --> 03:28.590
have to risk their lives
and jump off the cliff

03:28.590 --> 03:31.310
for living.

03:32.000 --> 03:33.440
From a hundred meters high,

03:33.440 --> 03:35.840
they have to
land on their softest bellies.

03:35.910 --> 03:37.840
Only the survivors can grow up.

03:39.280 --> 03:40.810
What about the adult birds?

03:41.760 --> 03:43.720
Do they just watch the little birds jump?

03:43.720 --> 03:44.880
They just watch.

03:45.370 --> 03:47.700
This is a lesson for every Barnacle Goose.

03:48.120 --> 03:49.310
But on second thought,

03:49.310 --> 03:51.470
they all survive on their own courage.

03:51.630 --> 03:53.430
So, they will always just be themselves,

03:53.430 --> 03:55.160
not someone else's appendage.

03:55.430 --> 03:57.310
One day, they will stand high up

03:57.310 --> 03:59.910
and look down on the abyss
they once conquered.

04:14.000 --> 04:15.470
I kindly told you a story.

04:15.750 --> 04:18.079
Are you secretly cursing me in your heart?

05:13.040 --> 05:14.510
[Xu Miyu, 18th floor,
Daily shift, Bad Review]

05:14.750 --> 05:15.560
Miyu.

05:15.920 --> 05:16.850
Where did you go?

05:18.300 --> 05:20.430
[Employee Schedule] [Staff Score]

05:20.920 --> 05:21.720
I...

05:21.920 --> 05:23.450
I had an emergency just now.

05:25.190 --> 05:27.190
You accompanied your parents, right?

05:27.190 --> 05:28.220
I heard

05:28.390 --> 05:30.270
even the security guards were called.

05:30.270 --> 05:31.930
That was a misunderstanding.

05:32.150 --> 05:33.800
It's fine now.

05:41.000 --> 05:42.159
Is it even a guess?

05:42.159 --> 05:43.950
It must be her parents.

05:43.970 --> 05:45.510
As an adult, she even has to

05:45.510 --> 05:48.950
ask her parents to
beat the mistress of her husband.

05:48.950 --> 05:50.680
She lives such a cowardly life.

05:52.720 --> 05:53.510
Miyu.

05:53.830 --> 05:55.070
The guest has checked out?

05:55.070 --> 05:55.800
He just left.

05:56.950 --> 05:59.190
The one who came to beat the mistress
wasn't my biological father,

05:59.190 --> 06:00.380
but my stepfather.

06:01.680 --> 06:02.490
And

06:03.160 --> 06:04.950
if you have any gossip
you want to ask about,

06:04.950 --> 06:05.950
I'm right here.

06:06.070 --> 06:07.070
No need to guess wildly.

06:07.070 --> 06:08.390
You can ask me directly.

06:08.390 --> 06:10.270
Miyu, I wasn't talking about you.

06:31.830 --> 06:33.230
Starting from the bottom

06:33.750 --> 06:35.310
may seem like a detour.

06:35.450 --> 06:36.930
But taking it step by step

06:36.950 --> 06:38.610
might be more down-to-earth.

06:39.000 --> 06:40.870
So, they will always just be themselves,

06:40.870 --> 06:42.130
not someone else's appendage.

06:42.130 --> 06:43.860
He holds a black card

06:43.890 --> 06:45.240
and stays on our executive floor.

06:45.240 --> 06:47.450
His judgement

06:47.480 --> 06:49.200
carries a lot of weight.

07:10.420 --> 07:11.650
Room service.

07:17.070 --> 07:18.510
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

07:19.390 --> 07:20.750
Is it convenient for me to come in

07:20.750 --> 07:22.410
and clean the room for you now?

07:22.630 --> 07:24.160
Then, I will start working.

07:41.190 --> 07:42.390
If you find it noisy,

07:42.390 --> 07:43.920
please wait in the bedroom first.

07:43.920 --> 07:45.159
I will clean your room
as quickly as possible.

07:45.159 --> 07:46.720
What are you doing?

07:47.600 --> 07:48.720
I'm cleaning.

07:50.310 --> 07:51.159
Can you be normal?

07:51.159 --> 07:52.159
Yes, sir.

07:54.270 --> 07:54.920
Okay.

08:21.390 --> 08:22.160
Mr. Ji,

08:22.160 --> 08:24.360
is there anything else you need me to do?

08:24.510 --> 08:26.430
You can leave after cleaning.

08:38.900 --> 08:40.030
Didn't I tell you to leave?

08:40.030 --> 08:41.909
I see you've been busy all morning.

08:41.909 --> 08:44.570
You may need a cup of coffee
to refresh yourself.

08:46.960 --> 08:49.200
My work is my own business.

08:49.510 --> 08:50.970
You've finished your work.

08:50.970 --> 08:51.970
You can leave now.

08:52.080 --> 08:52.720
Thank you.

08:52.720 --> 08:53.390
You can go.

08:59.840 --> 09:00.720
Mr. Ji,

09:00.720 --> 09:02.270
are you satisfied with my service?

09:02.270 --> 09:03.150
If the answer is yes,

09:03.150 --> 09:04.240
please give me a good review.

09:04.240 --> 09:04.870
Thank you.

09:06.760 --> 09:08.690
Why should I give you a good review?

09:09.630 --> 09:10.120
Your good review

09:10.120 --> 09:11.870
is the greatest encouragement for my work.

09:11.870 --> 09:12.720
Thank you.

09:15.860 --> 09:18.120
Are you playing tricks again?

09:21.120 --> 09:23.200
I... I haven't played any tricks.

09:24.200 --> 09:27.000
Last time at the birthday banquet
of Nie Yucheng's mother,

09:27.000 --> 09:28.550
my napkin fell on the floor,

09:28.960 --> 09:30.870
and I saw you under the table.

09:34.200 --> 09:35.840
That was a special situation.

09:35.840 --> 09:37.630
And justifiable, right?

09:39.510 --> 09:40.440
Mr. Ji,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.630
after you chatted with me last time,

09:42.630 --> 09:44.440
I thought you were absolutely right.

09:44.440 --> 09:45.630
I should set a new goal

09:45.630 --> 09:47.090
for my life.

09:47.110 --> 09:48.120
So,

09:48.120 --> 09:50.350
my current goal is to be a good attendant

09:50.510 --> 09:51.960
and get good reviews from guests.

09:51.960 --> 09:53.870
Isn't your goal a bit too small?

09:54.720 --> 09:55.910
Then, do you think

09:56.200 --> 09:58.480
setting my goal as
being the hotel general manager

09:58.480 --> 09:59.680
is easier to achieve?

10:02.720 --> 10:04.320
I... I just think

10:04.320 --> 10:06.720
I was too eager to start over

10:06.720 --> 10:07.960
and too impatient.

10:07.960 --> 10:10.440
Now I just want to take it step by step

10:10.440 --> 10:12.320
and do everything well at the moment.

10:12.320 --> 10:13.320
I want to start with

10:13.320 --> 10:15.450
getting a good review from you, Mr. Ji.

10:17.320 --> 10:20.960
Your service is merely okay at best.

10:21.720 --> 10:24.200
It's far from my standard
for a good review.

10:25.200 --> 10:26.840
Then, what is your standard?

10:29.550 --> 10:32.960
I... I sincerely want to ask you, Mr. Ji.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.200
Can you tell me

10:34.200 --> 10:35.480
the weakness

10:35.480 --> 10:36.960
of my service?

10:37.550 --> 10:38.550
You are over time.

10:39.080 --> 10:40.240
The standard time

10:40.390 --> 10:41.630
for cleaning a room is 20 minutes.

10:41.630 --> 10:44.320
You can only be meticulous
within 15 minutes.

10:44.550 --> 10:45.550
In the remaining five minutes,

10:45.550 --> 10:47.330
you have to do the final check.

10:48.000 --> 10:50.600
And the time you've spent in my room

10:50.880 --> 10:52.010
has been 23 minutes.

10:54.670 --> 10:56.320
I think there's a flaw in your standard.

10:56.320 --> 10:57.080
What flaw?

10:57.550 --> 10:58.960
The presidential suite upstairs

10:58.960 --> 11:00.440
covers 308 square meters.

11:00.720 --> 11:01.720
Cleaning it completely

11:01.720 --> 11:03.500
requires at least 30 minutes.

11:03.550 --> 11:05.080
Each room on the executive floor

11:05.080 --> 11:06.960
averages 78 square meters.

11:07.030 --> 11:09.150
It takes at least 25 minutes to clean.

11:09.150 --> 11:10.240
I think our service

11:10.240 --> 11:11.600
shouldn't just pursue speed.

11:11.600 --> 11:14.130
What's more important
is the service result.

11:14.160 --> 11:15.550
Then, let me make one thing clear to you.

11:15.550 --> 11:17.790
You are cleaning a guest's room

11:17.790 --> 11:18.990
but not your own home.

11:19.080 --> 11:21.150
Ensuring both efficiency and quality

11:21.150 --> 11:23.050
is the basic quality

11:23.080 --> 11:24.480
of a hotel service staff.

11:25.170 --> 11:26.170
If you can't do it,

11:26.220 --> 11:27.060
I suggest you

11:27.090 --> 11:27.720
go back

11:27.740 --> 11:30.270
and improve
your professional skills first.

11:30.870 --> 11:32.840
I can finish my work

11:32.840 --> 11:33.870
within the specified time.

11:33.870 --> 11:35.550
I just want to provide guests
with more meticulous

11:35.550 --> 11:36.150
and thoughtful service.

11:36.150 --> 11:36.840
Then, do you know

11:36.840 --> 11:39.040
what the first principle of service is?

11:39.480 --> 11:41.550
To provide guests with the most...

11:41.550 --> 11:42.720
It's not to disturb.

11:49.000 --> 11:49.720
Then,

11:50.120 --> 11:52.440
I won't disturb you.

11:59.630 --> 12:01.000
Good review.

12:08.030 --> 12:09.030
Good review.

12:09.740 --> 12:10.590
Good review.

12:11.750 --> 12:13.610
Do you think I want to disturb you?

12:18.120 --> 12:19.430
I didn't give you a good review,

12:19.430 --> 12:20.690
so you maliciously retaliated against me,
right?

12:20.690 --> 12:21.290
I...

12:22.490 --> 12:24.100
I didn't mean it.

12:36.600 --> 12:37.390
Miyu.

12:42.250 --> 12:44.710
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

12:44.270 --> 12:46.200
I got your dorm address,

12:46.200 --> 12:47.530
so I came to wait for you.

12:48.240 --> 12:49.840
Why did you just get off work?

12:49.870 --> 12:51.070
What do you want to do?

12:52.030 --> 12:53.870
I've been cleaning up
the house these days.

12:53.870 --> 12:55.150
There are some of your things.

12:55.150 --> 12:56.480
When Zhenzhen was cleaning,

12:56.480 --> 12:57.610
I saved them for you.

12:57.630 --> 12:58.390
The things I didn't take away

12:58.390 --> 12:59.870
are the things I don't want.

12:59.870 --> 13:01.070
Just throw them away.

13:03.750 --> 13:04.970
I'm here today

13:05.360 --> 13:06.890
to visit you specifically.

13:07.630 --> 13:09.150
Although we can't be a couple,

13:09.150 --> 13:11.630
we've been together
for over a decade after all.

13:11.630 --> 13:13.000
We can still be friends, right?

13:13.000 --> 13:14.270
There's no need to be so distant.

13:14.270 --> 13:15.750
There are some thick clothes inside.

13:14.350 --> 13:15.680
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

13:15.750 --> 13:16.630
Winter is coming.

13:16.630 --> 13:17.830
It's cold in the dorm.

13:18.630 --> 13:19.510
Just keep them.

13:19.870 --> 13:21.360
I don't want to see you

13:21.360 --> 13:23.160
having a hard time because of me.

13:30.420 --> 13:32.670
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

13:32.760 --> 13:34.290
Why did you throw them away?

13:34.480 --> 13:35.270
Nie Yucheng.

13:36.810 --> 13:38.750
Do you think a few words

13:38.750 --> 13:40.150
can trick me back?

13:41.600 --> 13:43.600
-No.
-I'm ready to sue you.

13:44.750 --> 13:45.680
What did you say?

13:45.790 --> 13:47.000
You still owe me four million yuan.

13:47.000 --> 13:48.860
You haven't forgotten, have you?

13:49.120 --> 13:50.240
I've made myself very clear to your lawyer

13:50.240 --> 13:51.750
about the whereabouts of the money.

13:51.750 --> 13:53.000
I don't have 4 million.

13:53.000 --> 13:54.080
Don't go too far.

13:54.080 --> 13:55.120
You know very well

13:55.120 --> 13:56.980
whether you have 4 million or not.

13:57.270 --> 13:59.000
We're going to court anyway.

13:59.240 --> 14:00.720
The law will give me justice.

14:00.720 --> 14:02.200
What justice?

14:03.030 --> 14:04.030
Every penny in this family

14:04.030 --> 14:05.790
was earned by me working my fingers
to the bone.

14:05.790 --> 14:06.870
I've supported you for so many years.

14:06.870 --> 14:08.390
I bought you everything you have.

14:08.390 --> 14:09.320
What have you done for me?

14:09.320 --> 14:10.390
What have you done for this family?

14:10.390 --> 14:11.750
How dare you ask me for money?

14:11.750 --> 14:12.870
Do you have any shame?

14:12.870 --> 14:14.270
You're shameless!

14:15.320 --> 14:16.150
Nie Yucheng,

14:16.870 --> 14:18.390
you've finally stopped acting.

14:18.390 --> 14:19.550
Have you lost your memory?

14:19.550 --> 14:21.320
We've been married for ten years.

14:21.320 --> 14:23.750
I did all the housework for a whole decade

14:23.750 --> 14:26.030
and took care of you 24/7.

14:26.030 --> 14:28.120
Even if you hire a nanny,
you have to pay her.

14:28.120 --> 14:28.790
Also,

14:28.790 --> 14:30.390
as your wife,

14:30.510 --> 14:32.670
I maintained your business relationships,

14:32.670 --> 14:33.720
curried favor with others,

14:33.720 --> 14:34.630
and helped you sign those orders

14:34.630 --> 14:36.440
worthy hundreds of thousands
or millions.

14:34.740 --> 14:36.360
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

14:36.470 --> 14:38.510
Now they are all the credit of you alone,
huh?

14:38.510 --> 14:39.790
Where is my salary?

14:39.790 --> 14:41.150
Xu Miyu, you…

14:41.150 --> 14:43.280
I'm going to make it clear to you today.

14:43.670 --> 14:45.200
I will go to court,

14:45.200 --> 14:46.740
and I will definitely win.

14:46.960 --> 14:49.550
This money belongs to the former Xu Miyu,

14:50.030 --> 14:51.630
and I will get it back for her.

14:53.150 --> 14:54.880
Now that you love money so much,

14:54.960 --> 14:56.890
why were you so eager to divorce me?

14:57.030 --> 14:58.690
You should have known better.

14:58.790 --> 15:00.410
If you were still Mrs. Nie,

15:00.440 --> 15:01.970
all my money would be yours.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.130
Even now,

15:05.550 --> 15:08.790
do you still think I care
about your money?

15:24.550 --> 15:26.200
Honey, you're back.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.510
I'm back.

15:28.550 --> 15:30.200
Did you buy this takeout?

15:31.200 --> 15:32.170
Yes.

15:32.390 --> 15:33.650
This is our dinner.

15:34.870 --> 15:36.200
Look, does it look good?

15:36.200 --> 15:38.200
I plan to wear this on my first day
of work tomorrow.

15:38.200 --> 15:39.270
It looks good.

15:39.270 --> 15:40.150
So beautiful.

15:40.790 --> 15:41.990
You didn't even look.

15:42.030 --> 15:43.080
You're so perfunctory.

15:43.080 --> 15:44.870
Let me have a look.

15:45.150 --> 15:45.790
Come on.

15:45.790 --> 15:47.250
Turn around and let me see.

15:48.790 --> 15:50.720
My wife looks good in everything.

15:51.030 --> 15:52.630
You're so sweet-talking.

15:53.200 --> 15:54.910
Did you throw away
what I asked you to throw?

15:54.910 --> 15:56.440
I threw them away.

15:56.510 --> 15:57.440
Why would I lie to you?

15:57.440 --> 15:58.550
Not necessarily.

15:58.750 --> 16:00.390
You never tell the truth.

16:02.670 --> 16:03.870
My wife

16:04.270 --> 16:06.670
is the woman who treats me best
in the world.

16:06.910 --> 16:09.030
I swear all my money

16:09.240 --> 16:11.200
and everything, including myself,

16:11.200 --> 16:12.660
belong to you and the baby.

16:13.080 --> 16:15.210
I will definitely give you happiness.

16:16.030 --> 16:17.030
What's up?

16:17.150 --> 16:18.030
Nothing.

16:18.270 --> 16:18.790
I suddenly realized

16:18.790 --> 16:20.920
that I haven't said these words to you.

16:21.870 --> 16:22.720
Okay then.

16:22.720 --> 16:25.080
You drop me off
at Purong for work tomorrow.

16:25.080 --> 16:25.920
Okay.

16:49.590 --> 16:53.660
[Purong Hotel]

16:57.260 --> 16:58.720
Mr. Ray, this way, please.

17:00.200 --> 17:00.550
Hello.

17:00.550 --> 17:01.840
I'm new in the sales department.

17:01.840 --> 17:02.960
I'm Lu Zhenzhen.

17:02.960 --> 17:03.670
Director Lu.

17:03.670 --> 17:06.069
Mr. Feng told me specifically this morning

17:06.069 --> 17:08.440
that a newly transferred supervisor
from the sales department

17:08.440 --> 17:10.720
brought a major client
to our executive floor,

17:10.720 --> 17:12.310
and asked us to treat him well.

17:12.310 --> 17:13.329
This is...

17:14.000 --> 17:15.310
This is Mr. Ray.

17:15.310 --> 17:16.829
He came from Malaysia to Shanghai

17:16.829 --> 17:19.440
as a cultural tourism commissioner
for a special inspection.

17:19.440 --> 17:20.349
Hello, sir.

17:20.349 --> 17:23.010
Welcome to the executive floor
of Purong Hotel.

17:23.030 --> 17:24.440
I will check you in now.

17:24.440 --> 17:26.310
Please show your ID.

17:34.440 --> 17:35.200
Ms. Zhang,

17:35.740 --> 17:36.940
Mr. Ray

17:36.960 --> 17:38.070
is in charge of

17:38.070 --> 17:39.720
corporate legal conferences in Malaysia.

17:39.720 --> 17:40.830
Throughout Southeast Asia,

17:40.830 --> 17:42.680
he has a lot of conference resources.

17:42.680 --> 17:45.010
Please make sure you take good care
of him this time.

17:45.010 --> 17:46.810
If he has a good stay experience,

17:47.070 --> 17:48.550
we will have many big orders.

17:48.550 --> 17:50.960
This is a new batch of aromatherapy
from our sales department.

17:50.960 --> 17:52.560
I'll give you a bottle to try.

17:53.440 --> 17:54.200
Director Lu,

17:54.590 --> 17:56.070
you are too kind.

17:56.070 --> 17:56.830
Don't worry.

17:57.070 --> 17:59.030
We will definitely use
the highest standards

17:59.030 --> 18:00.270
to receive your VIP.

18:00.310 --> 18:02.170
Please take good care of him then.

18:02.270 --> 18:03.600
Call Luo Qingping over.

18:04.200 --> 18:04.960
No need.

18:05.200 --> 18:06.070
Let it be her.

18:11.200 --> 18:12.810
This attendant is a newcomer.

18:12.810 --> 18:14.790
I'm afraid her service
might not be perfect.

18:14.790 --> 18:17.120
Newcomers need opportunities even more.

18:17.550 --> 18:18.480
Let her serve me.

18:21.720 --> 18:22.510
Miyu.

18:23.880 --> 18:24.720
Ms. Zhang.

18:26.830 --> 18:29.230
You are responsible for this guest's room.

18:33.270 --> 18:34.480
Glad to serve you.

18:35.070 --> 18:35.590
Mr. Ray

18:35.590 --> 18:37.240
is a major client of our sales department.

18:37.240 --> 18:38.840
Please take good care of him.

18:41.830 --> 18:42.830
I'll do it myself.

18:44.510 --> 18:45.550
The opportunity is given to you.

18:45.550 --> 18:46.830
I hope you cherish it.

18:48.310 --> 18:49.310
You must be tired from the journey.

18:49.310 --> 18:50.310
Let me do it.

18:50.830 --> 18:51.830
This way, please.

18:57.110 --> 18:59.310
Director Lu, rest assured.

18:59.310 --> 19:01.070
We will provide excellent service

19:01.070 --> 19:04.070
and cooperate seamlessly
with the sales department.

19:15.550 --> 19:17.080
Let me open the door for you.

19:20.790 --> 19:21.650
Please come in.

19:24.000 --> 19:24.640
Miss,

19:24.830 --> 19:26.090
can I have your WeChat?

19:26.550 --> 19:27.640
I'm sorry, sir.

19:27.640 --> 19:28.590
Our hotel has a rule

19:28.590 --> 19:30.640
that we can't add guests' contact
information without permission.

19:30.640 --> 19:31.920
If you have any needs,

19:31.920 --> 19:33.830
dial the phone by the bed.

19:33.880 --> 19:35.750
I just think you are very nice.

19:35.830 --> 19:37.160
I hope during my stay,

19:37.160 --> 19:38.820
you will be the one serving me.

19:40.310 --> 19:40.920
I'm sorry.

19:40.920 --> 19:42.240
I have to follow our rule.

19:42.240 --> 19:43.590
In other hotels,

19:43.830 --> 19:45.830
the butlers would give me
their contact information.

19:45.830 --> 19:47.030
Is Purong

19:47.310 --> 19:49.310
being a bit disrespectful to
the guests?

19:49.310 --> 19:50.570
Then I won't stay here.

19:51.160 --> 19:52.810
I'll change to a hotel
with better service.

19:52.810 --> 19:53.730
Sir,

19:53.920 --> 19:55.640
let me add your contact.

20:00.400 --> 20:02.590
Just let me know if you need anything.

20:07.170 --> 20:08.400
Just tell me,

20:08.400 --> 20:10.270
is the big boss of Kuanli coming?

20:10.270 --> 20:11.310
Yeah.

20:11.310 --> 20:11.830
Exactly.

20:11.830 --> 20:13.640
Stop guessing.

20:13.640 --> 20:15.070
Do you know the scale of Kuanli?

20:15.070 --> 20:16.400
The big boss of Kuanli, Duan Longyun,

20:16.400 --> 20:18.830
manages dozens of companies nationwide.

20:18.920 --> 20:20.070
If he really stayed upstairs,

20:20.070 --> 20:22.000
who would manage those companies?

20:22.920 --> 20:25.830
But there's definitely a reason
for keeping you busy.

20:25.830 --> 20:28.310
He's not the only Boss Duan
in Kuanli Group.

20:28.640 --> 20:31.070
Could it be the younger Boss Duan,
Duan Aoxiang?

20:31.070 --> 20:32.110
I never said that.

20:32.110 --> 20:33.270
It's him.

20:33.270 --> 20:34.350
I really like him.

20:34.350 --> 20:35.480
Me too.

20:35.480 --> 20:37.550
He's both a noble gentleman
and a popular star.

20:37.550 --> 20:38.880
I really like him too.

20:39.000 --> 20:40.480
Look at you all.

20:40.480 --> 20:41.340
Let me tell you,

20:41.400 --> 20:42.060
Mr. Duan Jr.

20:42.090 --> 20:43.310
has a master's degree

20:43.310 --> 20:44.480
in hotel management

20:44.480 --> 20:45.550
from the University of Birmingham.

20:45.550 --> 20:47.750
The gambling agreement
with Purong Hotel

20:47.750 --> 20:49.550
is a project he led.

20:50.240 --> 20:51.440
Maybe in a year,

20:51.440 --> 20:52.880
he will be your boss.

20:59.070 --> 20:59.750
Sir,

21:00.480 --> 21:02.210
this place has been booked out.

21:09.110 --> 21:09.880
Sir,

21:11.480 --> 21:13.480
this place has also been booked out.

21:14.030 --> 21:15.510
This is a public area.

21:15.510 --> 21:16.680
How can it be booked out?

21:16.680 --> 21:17.550
Besides,

21:17.550 --> 21:18.720
in the time you're stopping me,

21:18.720 --> 21:20.110
I could have finished a cup of coffee.

21:20.110 --> 21:20.830
Actually,

21:20.830 --> 21:22.110
the VIP will arrive at any time.

21:22.110 --> 21:22.720
How about you go...

21:22.720 --> 21:24.510
I said this is a public area.

21:24.720 --> 21:26.120
Don't you understand me?

21:26.480 --> 21:27.240
I understand.

21:27.240 --> 21:29.480
Do you always drive away
all the guests in the hotel

21:29.480 --> 21:31.030
every time you receive a VIP?

21:31.030 --> 21:32.590
Sorry.

21:32.790 --> 21:33.550
What's up?

21:34.310 --> 21:36.030
Mr. Wei said to clear the area,

21:36.310 --> 21:39.510
but this gentleman insists on
having a cup of coffee here.

21:40.110 --> 21:40.830
Go ahead.

21:40.830 --> 21:41.760
Leave this to me.

21:51.640 --> 21:53.370
You can't recognize me, right?

21:54.750 --> 21:56.030
Indeed, I can't.

21:57.720 --> 21:58.520
I grew up ugly.

22:03.110 --> 22:04.160
Senior Xue Rui.

22:06.310 --> 22:07.920
Long time no see.

22:13.200 --> 22:14.660
How many years has it been?

22:14.830 --> 22:15.830
Ten years, right?

22:15.920 --> 22:16.960
Ten years.

22:19.770 --> 22:20.720
Come, leader.

22:20.720 --> 22:22.550
Xue, pour the wine.

22:23.750 --> 22:25.110
Mr. Liu,

22:25.750 --> 22:28.610
thank you for your bank's great support
for my work.

22:28.760 --> 22:30.310
I toast you.

22:30.310 --> 22:31.110
Chug!
You can drink as much as you want.

22:31.110 --> 22:32.070
Come on.

22:32.470 --> 22:33.270
Please.

22:36.240 --> 22:37.070
Good.

22:37.070 --> 22:37.970
Good drinker.

22:42.240 --> 22:42.750
Come on.

22:42.260 --> 22:43.370
[Young Xue Rui]

22:42.750 --> 22:43.830
Everyone, cheers.

22:43.830 --> 22:45.070
Thank you for coming. Come on.

22:45.070 --> 22:45.640
Xue, come on.

22:45.640 --> 22:46.310
Pour the drinks.

22:46.310 --> 22:46.830
Hurry.

22:48.110 --> 22:48.750
Come on.

22:49.310 --> 22:50.400
Thank you all.

22:50.400 --> 22:51.720
Let's continue to cooperate.

22:51.720 --> 22:52.510
Come on, together.

22:52.510 --> 22:53.000
Cheers. Come on.

22:53.000 --> 22:54.920
Thanks to your help
back then, senior.

22:54.920 --> 22:57.270
Or I would be kicked out as a rookie.

22:57.300 --> 22:59.700
Thanks to you, I completed the internship.

23:00.270 --> 23:03.070
In the blink of an eye,
the rookie has become a boss.

23:03.760 --> 23:04.460
By the way.

23:04.720 --> 23:06.790
I remember you've been abroad.

23:06.790 --> 23:08.050
When did you come back?

23:08.880 --> 23:10.350
Not long ago.

23:11.030 --> 23:12.230
What brings you here?

23:12.270 --> 23:13.400
First,

23:13.960 --> 23:15.720
take a vacation and rest.

23:18.070 --> 23:20.160
Do you want to go to my office?

23:21.070 --> 23:22.030
Director Xue.

23:22.550 --> 23:23.160
Coming.

23:23.270 --> 23:25.480
Mr. Wei asked us
to gather at the VIP channel.

23:25.480 --> 23:26.270
Hurry up.

23:26.400 --> 23:26.880
Okay.

23:27.480 --> 23:28.030
How about this?

23:28.030 --> 23:28.550
I'll get back to work.

23:28.550 --> 23:30.480
I'll find you after I'm done today.

23:31.880 --> 23:33.480
I have a big family here.

23:33.480 --> 23:34.640
How are we supposed to move?

23:34.640 --> 23:35.880
We will help you pack.

23:35.880 --> 23:37.030
You just need to move.

23:37.030 --> 23:38.350
We can give you a discount
on the room rate,

23:38.350 --> 23:40.210
a 50% discount. What do you think?

23:40.480 --> 23:41.750
A 50% discount?

23:43.030 --> 23:44.440
Can you make it a 60% discount?

23:44.440 --> 23:45.480
I'm sorry, sir.

23:45.480 --> 23:47.440
This price is set by our director.

23:48.960 --> 23:50.400
Hello, room service.

23:51.680 --> 23:53.160
Hello, Mr. Ji.

23:54.240 --> 23:55.240
Mr. Ji.

23:57.110 --> 23:58.200
He's dead asleep?

24:02.200 --> 24:03.550
Who are you talking about?

24:03.550 --> 24:04.570
Mr. Ji,

24:04.790 --> 24:06.820
is it okay for you to
change to a new room?

24:06.820 --> 24:08.440
The subsequent room rate will be 50% off.

24:08.440 --> 24:09.700
Why do I need to change?

24:10.960 --> 24:12.510
The water pipe
on the executive floor is broken.

24:12.510 --> 24:14.680
The Engineering Department
needs to repair it.

24:14.680 --> 24:15.480
Where is it broken?

24:15.480 --> 24:16.750
Take me to see it.

24:18.400 --> 24:19.720
That's the Engineering
Department's business.

24:19.720 --> 24:22.160
We attendants are only responsible
for communication.

24:22.160 --> 24:23.270
That's nonsense.

24:24.000 --> 24:27.130
Then when is it convenient
for you to change to a new room?

24:28.350 --> 24:30.680
When is it convenient for you, please?

24:30.680 --> 24:33.940
Watch out, I'll complain about you
disturbing the guests.

24:37.350 --> 24:38.160
What are you doing?

24:38.160 --> 24:39.350
This is my job.

24:39.350 --> 24:40.710
Find someone else to talk to me.

24:40.710 --> 24:41.400
Move aside.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.790
The renovation concept of Purong Hotel is

24:56.790 --> 24:57.480
sharpness.

24:57.920 --> 25:00.240
Radormok white marble

25:00.240 --> 25:02.070
paired with black agate and pure gold

25:02.070 --> 25:03.240
seems bright and noble,

25:02.170 --> 25:04.440
[Lobby area]

25:03.240 --> 25:04.270
and magnificent.

25:04.440 --> 25:10.620
[Space Design]

25:04.510 --> 25:06.030
As for the original crystal
lighting of Purong,

25:06.030 --> 25:07.350
we have kept it.

25:07.350 --> 25:08.480
But for things like

25:08.480 --> 25:11.590
the complicated geometric splicing
on the walls,

25:11.590 --> 25:12.270
we will consider

25:12.270 --> 25:14.960
replacing it with large blocks
of color later.

25:15.000 --> 25:17.400
Then, what's the difference
between this and

25:17.400 --> 25:19.030
the Kuanli Dinghui Resort Hotel

25:19.030 --> 25:20.440
we built in Shenzhen before?

25:20.440 --> 25:21.440
Mr. Duan, this...

25:21.440 --> 25:23.370
It doesn't sound very innovative.

25:23.720 --> 25:25.030
Innovation...

25:25.030 --> 25:26.490
The innovation lies in...

25:31.640 --> 25:32.200
Sorry.

25:32.200 --> 25:33.200
I didn't hear you.

25:33.640 --> 25:37.040
The innovation lies in the difference
in internal modeling.

25:40.270 --> 25:41.270
What I want is

25:41.440 --> 25:42.350
very simple.

25:44.960 --> 25:45.640
Mr. Duan,

25:45.640 --> 25:48.240
only what hasn't been seen
before is shocking.

25:48.920 --> 25:50.620
Tell your boss later.

25:50.750 --> 25:52.880
Stop fooling me with ideas
from ten years ago.

25:52.880 --> 25:53.640
Okay.

25:53.720 --> 25:54.720
I will go back and report.

25:54.720 --> 25:56.160
We make a new design for you.

25:56.160 --> 25:57.480
That's your business.

25:59.790 --> 26:00.680
Are you hungry?

26:02.790 --> 26:03.390
Let's go.

26:11.270 --> 26:13.110
-Mr. Duan.
-Mr. Duan.

26:13.110 --> 26:15.160
-Mr. Duan Jr.
-Mr. Duan Jr.

26:16.750 --> 26:19.200
Welcome.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.640
I specially reserved
the presidential suite for you,

26:22.640 --> 26:23.640
is it okay?

26:23.750 --> 26:26.000
Only you have the qualification
to stay in the suite.

26:26.000 --> 26:27.750
Is it the suite where
the president has stayed?

26:27.750 --> 26:29.480
I'm enjoying the honor, huh?

26:30.590 --> 26:31.310
By the way,

26:32.400 --> 26:34.270
hurry up with the supplementary agreement.

26:34.270 --> 26:35.530
You haven't signed it.

26:35.640 --> 26:36.720
I'm afraid that there will be changes.

26:36.720 --> 26:38.720
You must be joking. How would I dare?

26:38.960 --> 26:41.490
It's just that the details
still need to be refined.

26:41.490 --> 26:43.200
As long as you don't change your mind,

26:43.200 --> 26:44.960
I am absolutely loyal.

26:44.960 --> 26:45.640
That's good.

26:45.640 --> 26:46.790
And there is the same issue

26:46.790 --> 26:47.720
I've mentioned.

26:47.720 --> 26:49.510
Everything that can be solved with money

26:49.510 --> 26:50.200
is not a big deal.

26:50.200 --> 26:52.160
I understand. I know this.

26:52.160 --> 26:53.750
Mr. Duan.

26:54.420 --> 26:56.020
Just one minute of your time.

26:56.020 --> 26:58.150
The executive floor has been cleared.

26:58.200 --> 26:59.080
But...

26:59.110 --> 26:59.920
But what?

27:00.270 --> 27:01.720
Didn't I say to waive all bills?

27:01.720 --> 27:03.480
I did so.

27:04.110 --> 27:06.480
The other guests all happily moved out.

27:06.640 --> 27:07.960
Only one person is left.

27:07.960 --> 27:09.510
Then give him a large amount of money.

27:09.510 --> 27:12.200
Everything that can be solved with money
is not a big deal.

27:12.200 --> 27:13.000
Yes, I know.

27:13.440 --> 27:16.230
But this person probably
doesn't want money.

27:16.350 --> 27:17.640
Who?

27:17.640 --> 27:18.350
Who is it?

27:18.350 --> 27:19.480
You can't handle it?

27:20.790 --> 27:21.920
Doesn't want money?

27:22.160 --> 27:22.960
Interesting.

27:24.440 --> 27:26.240
Then I'll go meet this tough nut.

27:45.240 --> 27:46.170
Hello, Mr. Duan.

27:48.510 --> 27:49.440
Hello, Mr. Duan.

27:59.480 --> 28:00.410
Hello, Mr. Duan.

28:09.830 --> 28:10.640
Sir,

28:10.640 --> 28:12.840
please cooperate and change your room.

28:13.920 --> 28:14.830
Who are you?

28:14.830 --> 28:15.680
As for money,

28:15.680 --> 28:17.680
you can make any demands you want.

28:18.200 --> 28:20.400
Are you from the Engineering Department

28:20.400 --> 28:22.400
or another department of the hotel?

28:24.400 --> 28:25.820
If you are not hotel staff,

28:25.820 --> 28:27.670
you have no right to talk
to me about this.

28:27.670 --> 28:28.670
Wait.

28:33.200 --> 28:34.590
Don't you recognize me?

28:35.270 --> 28:36.750
Mr. Duan is here.

28:36.750 --> 28:39.200
I thought it was some young punk

28:39.200 --> 28:41.400
who didn't know his place
trying to mess with me.

28:41.400 --> 28:42.680
So, it's you after all.

28:42.680 --> 28:45.030
If you want to meet me, just contact me.

28:45.110 --> 28:46.590
Why put on such a big show

28:46.590 --> 28:47.960
and have so many people
play along with you?

28:47.960 --> 28:49.560
Mr. Duan, you like a big show,

28:49.840 --> 28:52.440
so the welcome gift should
cater to your taste.

28:54.960 --> 28:56.440
Old classmate,

28:56.480 --> 28:57.610
I missed you so much.

28:59.270 --> 28:59.720
This is

28:59.720 --> 29:01.790
my classmate and

29:01.790 --> 29:02.590
my good buddy in Birmingham.

29:02.590 --> 29:03.310
Call him Mr. Ji.

29:03.310 --> 29:04.920
Hello, Mr. Ji.

29:05.540 --> 29:06.960
Such a big show.

29:06.960 --> 29:08.960
Are they celebrating downstairs?

29:09.580 --> 29:11.110
What is there to celebrate?

29:14.030 --> 29:16.570
What do you think I'm celebrating?

29:16.880 --> 29:19.270
Kuanli Group invested in Purong Hotel

29:19.270 --> 29:20.790
and reached a strategic partnership?

29:20.790 --> 29:22.070
This is all trending.

29:22.310 --> 29:24.240
It's not surprising to celebrate.

29:24.610 --> 29:25.630
It seems

29:25.750 --> 29:27.170
you really don't know anything.

29:27.170 --> 29:28.640
I was never part of this to begin with.

29:28.640 --> 29:29.980
You're no outsider.

29:30.010 --> 29:31.310
You are my best buddy

29:31.310 --> 29:32.150
from my time in Birmingham.

29:32.150 --> 29:32.830
Let's go.

29:32.830 --> 29:34.030
Join the fun with me.

29:34.550 --> 29:36.550
Does the water pipe need to be fixed?

29:37.030 --> 29:38.480
Still got a sharp tongue.

29:38.480 --> 29:39.350
We're not fixing it.

29:39.350 --> 29:40.400
Even if we did,

29:40.400 --> 29:42.200
we'd skip your room,

29:42.200 --> 29:43.270
okay? Let's go.

29:43.810 --> 29:44.490
Wait.

29:44.790 --> 29:45.960
You're in a suit.

29:45.960 --> 29:47.000
I need to change.

29:47.440 --> 29:48.450
It's a celebration banquet.

29:48.450 --> 29:49.380
You've changed.

29:49.830 --> 29:52.070
But I like it more and more.

29:52.680 --> 29:54.640
Hurry up, I'll wait for you.

29:54.640 --> 29:55.440
Okay.

30:04.510 --> 30:07.240
You two will go help
in the executive lounge today.

30:07.240 --> 30:07.880
I am a newcomer.

30:07.880 --> 30:09.310
I'm not very familiar with

30:09.310 --> 30:11.000
the service process
of the executive lounge yet.

30:11.000 --> 30:12.110
It's okay.

30:12.110 --> 30:14.270
You work carefully
and have a good attitude.

30:14.270 --> 30:15.800
You'll definitely be fine.

30:16.510 --> 30:17.200
But I...

30:17.200 --> 30:18.270
Let me tell you.

30:18.270 --> 30:20.980
All the guests on the spot today are VIPs.

30:21.070 --> 30:22.640
If you can get

30:22.640 --> 30:23.720
a good review from them,

30:23.720 --> 30:24.790
your two bad reviews

30:24.790 --> 30:27.110
might be offset.

30:43.270 --> 30:45.270
Does he think he is Prince Charming?

31:03.240 --> 31:04.070
Thank you.

31:09.960 --> 31:11.400
Speak of the devil.

31:11.400 --> 31:12.350
Come here.

31:14.400 --> 31:15.000
This is

31:15.000 --> 31:17.060
Ji Feng, whom I was mentioned before.

31:18.110 --> 31:19.440
Ji Feng is my classmate,

31:19.960 --> 31:23.640
an all-rounder in hotel management
from the University of Birmingham.

31:23.640 --> 31:24.400
Mr. Wei,

31:24.790 --> 31:25.720
long time no see.

31:26.310 --> 31:27.640
You two know each other?

31:27.920 --> 31:30.030
I used to work at Purong Hotel

31:30.030 --> 31:32.110
and met with
Mr. Wei a few times.

31:32.270 --> 31:34.550
You once worked at Purong?

31:35.000 --> 31:36.240
How did I not know that?

31:36.240 --> 31:37.770
It was before I went abroad.

31:41.200 --> 31:42.550
I've heard Mr. Duan Jr. say

31:42.550 --> 31:44.070
that he has someone very capable with him,

31:44.070 --> 31:47.200
who's been managing
top-tier luxury hotels overseas for years.

31:47.200 --> 31:48.590
So, you were talking about Ji Feng.

31:48.590 --> 31:49.070
Yeah.

31:49.070 --> 31:50.600
Then we go way back.

31:50.790 --> 31:53.350
If I were not Mr. Duan's
former classmate,

31:53.350 --> 31:55.110
I wouldn't have gotten in today.

31:55.110 --> 31:56.550
No way, you're joking.

31:56.550 --> 31:58.440
You don't know this, Mr. Duan Jr.

31:58.440 --> 31:59.960
When Ji Feng worked at Purong,

31:59.960 --> 32:01.440
he was an outstanding employee.

32:01.440 --> 32:03.400
He is capable and popular.

32:03.400 --> 32:04.400
I always said

32:04.440 --> 32:06.880
he'd be a great talent
in hotel management.

32:07.030 --> 32:09.030
Now that you've got
some overseas experience,

32:09.030 --> 32:11.960
maybe I should be calling you Mr. Ji.

32:12.590 --> 32:13.920
Mr. Wei, you flatter me.

32:14.030 --> 32:15.110
Well, isn't that a coincidence?

32:15.110 --> 32:15.920
Next year,

32:16.200 --> 32:17.730
come be my general manager.

32:17.920 --> 32:19.480
Of what?

32:19.590 --> 32:20.530
Purong.

32:21.880 --> 32:23.100
So confident.

32:23.240 --> 32:24.720
Looks like investment
is just the appetizer,

32:24.720 --> 32:26.440
and acquisition is the main course.

32:26.440 --> 32:27.110
Smart.

32:28.030 --> 32:29.200
Mr. Duan Jr.,

32:29.370 --> 32:31.140
don't speak too soon.

32:31.270 --> 32:33.550
Although our hotel has
some operational issues,

32:33.550 --> 32:35.030
we still have a year

32:35.030 --> 32:35.960
to turn things around.

32:35.960 --> 32:37.550
Come on, Mr. Wei,

32:37.550 --> 32:38.310
easy.

32:38.440 --> 32:39.240
Anyway,

32:39.240 --> 32:40.110
Ji Feng

32:40.110 --> 32:40.960
isn't an outsider either.

32:40.960 --> 32:41.720
What are you afraid of?

32:41.720 --> 32:42.680
Besides,

32:42.680 --> 32:43.920
handing Purong over to me,

32:43.920 --> 32:44.880
you won't lose out.

32:44.880 --> 32:45.880
Yes.

32:46.160 --> 32:47.030
With you backing it,

32:47.030 --> 32:48.230
what do I have to fear?

32:48.640 --> 32:49.700
We're all friends.

32:50.640 --> 32:52.640
Well, you guys chat.

32:52.640 --> 32:53.720
I have things to do.

32:54.640 --> 32:55.500
I'll get going.

33:10.920 --> 33:12.030
Look into Ji Feng,

33:12.590 --> 33:14.450
and see what he's really back for.

33:14.550 --> 33:15.350
Okay.

33:19.200 --> 33:21.510
I heard you left Siwei Group

33:23.000 --> 33:25.260
and then swallowed sand for three years.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.590
It's good to be back.

33:26.590 --> 33:28.790
There's gold everywhere in our country.

33:28.790 --> 33:30.250
Where are you working now?

33:30.720 --> 33:32.310
I didn't make great achievements.

33:32.310 --> 33:33.400
Just slack off for now.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.800
You're fooling me again.

33:35.200 --> 33:36.480
Actually, when I saw you today,

33:36.480 --> 33:38.210
I was thinking about one thing.

33:38.550 --> 33:39.500
Why are you here?

33:39.790 --> 33:40.990
Just take a vacation.

33:41.310 --> 33:43.240
No need to rack your brains over it.

33:44.440 --> 33:45.270
Alright then.

33:46.030 --> 33:47.350
After your vacation,

33:47.350 --> 33:48.400
come work for me.

33:48.830 --> 33:50.030
Just name your price.

33:50.070 --> 33:50.640
It's the same to

33:50.640 --> 33:51.570
work for anyone.

33:52.480 --> 33:54.410
Mr. Duan, who is this?

33:54.880 --> 33:55.960
Let me introduce.

33:56.110 --> 33:56.720
This is

33:56.720 --> 33:59.980
Ji Feng, the top manager of Siwei Group,

34:00.270 --> 34:02.110
and my classmate
when I studied in Birmingham.

34:02.110 --> 34:03.480
Back in school,

34:03.480 --> 34:04.680
he was in first place,

34:04.830 --> 34:05.760
and I was second.

34:05.880 --> 34:07.110
We

34:07.110 --> 34:09.880
were known as the Dual Heroes
of Birmingham.

34:09.880 --> 34:12.050
This nickname combining East and West

34:12.080 --> 34:13.190
isn't very credible.

34:13.190 --> 34:14.880
Don't sabotage my efforts.

34:16.400 --> 34:17.280
Don't just stand there.

34:17.280 --> 34:19.360
Let's go taste today's main dish.

34:19.710 --> 34:20.400
Let's go.

34:20.670 --> 34:21.360
Let's go.

34:32.590 --> 34:33.550
These were shipped

34:33.550 --> 34:35.679
fresh from Europe early this morning.

34:43.550 --> 34:44.480
Have a taste.

34:48.150 --> 34:49.400
This taste...

34:54.670 --> 34:55.469
It's not good.

34:55.710 --> 34:57.550
Chef, take away all the caviar.

34:57.670 --> 34:58.440
Change it.

35:03.640 --> 35:05.150
Call Li Qiaoqi over here, quick.

35:05.150 --> 35:05.880
Okay.

35:09.700 --> 35:10.530
Qiaoqi,

35:10.560 --> 35:12.110
the guest in the executive lounge upstairs

35:12.110 --> 35:13.590
wants you to make a seafood feast.

35:13.590 --> 35:14.400
I'm not going.

35:14.710 --> 35:16.480
With those big boxes of caviar there,

35:16.480 --> 35:18.320
they can eat anything with it and be full.

35:18.320 --> 35:19.230
I'll just have some shrimp here.

35:19.230 --> 35:20.000
You have to.

35:20.000 --> 35:20.840
Qiaoqi,

35:20.840 --> 35:23.550
the boss upstairs said he doesn't want
the caviar feast anymore,

35:23.550 --> 35:26.280
and wants delicacies from land and sea.

35:26.510 --> 35:27.320
What the heck?

35:27.320 --> 35:28.650
That's such a long name.

35:30.440 --> 35:32.750
I want to see who's causing trouble.

35:32.840 --> 35:33.550
Let's go.

35:36.030 --> 35:37.230
I will definitely

35:38.230 --> 35:39.490
acquire Purong Hotel.

35:40.670 --> 35:41.440
Since when did Mr. Duan become

35:41.440 --> 35:42.630
so career-driven?

35:43.360 --> 35:44.800
My father

35:44.800 --> 35:45.880
finds fault with me every day.

35:45.880 --> 35:46.710
He said

35:46.710 --> 35:49.360
if I don't show him
some results this time,

35:49.400 --> 35:51.600
he might kick me out of the house one day.

35:52.230 --> 35:53.190
This time,

35:53.190 --> 35:54.480
this Purong project

35:54.480 --> 35:56.280
was single-handedly dug up by me.

35:56.280 --> 35:57.540
I think this will work.

35:59.400 --> 36:02.460
Why did you decide to
deal with such a troublesome case?

36:02.550 --> 36:03.940
Purong Hotel

36:04.550 --> 36:06.840
is a grand old hotel in Shanghai.

36:06.920 --> 36:08.710
It just looks strong on the outside.

36:08.710 --> 36:10.840
Go look at their financial report
from last year.

36:10.840 --> 36:12.550
They had a loss of 47 percent.

36:12.670 --> 36:13.550
If they want to

36:13.550 --> 36:16.320
make a 30 percent profit within a year,

36:16.400 --> 36:18.200
achieving an 80 percent growth,

36:18.400 --> 36:19.530
they need a miracle.

36:21.070 --> 36:21.880
Trust me.

36:22.230 --> 36:23.360
Purong Hotel

36:23.360 --> 36:25.230
will definitely be mine in a year.

36:25.630 --> 36:26.360
No suspense.

36:28.280 --> 36:29.140
Old classmate,

36:29.660 --> 36:31.740
nothing is certain in this world.

36:32.800 --> 36:34.510
But you won't lose out either way.

36:34.510 --> 36:36.240
Even if you don't get the hotel,

36:36.240 --> 36:38.030
you still get a high return rate
in one year.

36:38.030 --> 36:38.710
You make a lot of money too.

36:38.710 --> 36:40.120
Who cares about this little money?

36:40.120 --> 36:41.480
What I want is the entire hotel,

36:41.480 --> 36:42.560
the whole building.

36:42.560 --> 36:43.850
Just for

36:43.920 --> 36:46.030
that Presidential Suite,
where a few presidents have stayed,

36:46.030 --> 36:47.340
I must get it.

36:47.670 --> 36:48.760
When the time comes,

36:48.760 --> 36:49.890
you can work with me,

36:49.960 --> 36:52.220
and we will create brilliance together.

36:52.220 --> 36:53.260
It's a deal,

36:53.880 --> 36:55.160
no going back.

37:01.550 --> 37:02.550
The person

37:02.710 --> 37:04.150
in the red suit

37:04.150 --> 37:06.070
is Mr. Duan Jr. from the Kuanli Group.

37:06.070 --> 37:07.670
He threw today's party too.

37:08.190 --> 37:09.360
Making last-minute changes

37:09.360 --> 37:11.270
was his idea.

37:11.400 --> 37:12.190
I hate these

37:12.190 --> 37:14.720
rich kids whose brains
are soaked in alcohol.

37:14.760 --> 37:16.760
He delayed me from getting off work.

38:08.280 --> 38:09.230
Ya, Luo,

38:14.510 --> 38:15.400
thank you.

38:15.670 --> 38:17.920
It's delicious.

38:18.400 --> 38:19.240
Awesome.

38:19.280 --> 38:20.070
Smells good.

38:20.800 --> 38:21.800
BBQ.

38:21.800 --> 38:22.860
This is a good idea.

38:24.320 --> 38:25.800
I'll go get some drinks.

38:37.670 --> 38:38.760
Ya.

38:40.550 --> 38:41.550
Come in and get the raw marinated food.

38:41.550 --> 38:42.030
Okay.

38:45.070 --> 38:45.840
Luo.

38:46.150 --> 38:47.000
Come help.

38:47.960 --> 38:49.160
Here, take this over.

38:52.110 --> 38:52.550
Hurry up.

38:52.550 --> 38:53.110
Okay.

39:14.360 --> 39:15.360
Why is it all gone?

39:15.510 --> 39:17.150
Chef, please make some more.

39:19.070 --> 39:20.440
Sorry, I'm off work.

39:20.670 --> 39:21.960
Ya, let's go.

39:21.960 --> 39:22.760
Okay.

39:30.850 --> 39:31.890
Master Qiaoqi.

39:32.070 --> 39:32.630
Master Qiaoqi.

39:32.630 --> 39:33.480
Wait, wait.

39:34.400 --> 39:35.410
Wait, wait.

39:35.430 --> 39:36.500
What's wrong?

39:36.530 --> 39:37.990
I've finished all my work.

39:38.150 --> 39:39.110
Master Qiaoqi.

39:39.760 --> 39:41.510
The guests are praising your cooking.

39:41.510 --> 39:42.840
Show them a little more.

39:43.480 --> 39:45.110
Don't leave all the work to me.

39:45.110 --> 39:46.120
Where's Chef Jia?

39:46.230 --> 39:47.110
He's the head chef.

39:47.110 --> 39:48.570
Let him grill the skewers.

39:49.030 --> 39:49.880
Master Qiaoqi.

39:49.880 --> 39:51.190
Please don't make it difficult for me.

39:51.190 --> 39:52.590
The guest specifically asked for you.

39:52.590 --> 39:54.590
He's the financial backer of our hotel.

39:54.590 --> 39:56.520
Even the boss has to treat him well.

39:57.590 --> 39:59.080
Financial backer?

39:59.360 --> 40:00.840
Has he paid me overtime?

40:01.420 --> 40:03.880
Master Qiaoqi, thank you
for your hard work.

40:06.840 --> 40:07.760
Miyu.

40:23.760 --> 40:24.510
Thank you.

40:33.030 --> 40:34.760
Why is it all champagne?

40:34.760 --> 40:35.840
Is there no red wine?

40:35.840 --> 40:36.630
There's red wine over there,

40:36.630 --> 40:37.830
at the buffet table.

40:38.670 --> 40:39.510
Waiter.

40:42.920 --> 40:44.000
Hello, waiter.

40:47.000 --> 40:48.710
I'm sorry.

40:48.710 --> 40:49.510
Are you okay?

40:50.070 --> 40:51.110
Thank you, sir.

40:51.110 --> 40:53.640
Otherwise, I would have
fallen to the ground.

40:54.150 --> 40:57.000
Your suit must be expensive.

40:57.000 --> 40:58.510
I'm really sorry.

40:58.630 --> 40:59.150
Come on.

40:59.360 --> 41:01.020
It doesn't matter, it's fine.

41:03.140 --> 41:04.260
Mr. Ji,

41:04.290 --> 41:06.870
did you just come back from abroad?

41:08.670 --> 41:09.510
Do you know me?

41:09.670 --> 41:11.360
Everyone here knows you.

41:11.510 --> 41:12.840
You are Mr. Duan's friend,

41:12.840 --> 41:14.280
Mr. Ji Feng,

41:14.880 --> 41:16.840
the star manager of Siwei Group.

41:17.400 --> 41:18.460
Just an acting one.

41:18.670 --> 41:19.840
Mr. Ji.

41:19.840 --> 41:23.070
We are so destined to meet.

41:23.070 --> 41:24.960
Why don't we exchange WeChat?

41:28.320 --> 41:29.450
I'll scan your code.

41:34.050 --> 41:35.890
[Personal Receipt code]

41:34.320 --> 41:36.000
What do you mean?

41:36.030 --> 41:37.320
Adding a contact is too troublesome.

41:37.320 --> 41:38.190
This is more direct.

41:38.190 --> 41:40.000
No, you misunderstood.

41:40.110 --> 41:42.590
I just wanted to add you
as my WeChat friend

41:42.880 --> 41:44.550
to ask for your advice

41:44.550 --> 41:45.800
on some professional matters.

41:45.800 --> 41:46.260
Sure.

41:46.480 --> 41:48.400
Pay me the dry-cleaning fee first.

41:48.400 --> 41:49.360
This custom suit of mine

41:49.360 --> 41:50.920
costs 3,280 yuan to wash once.

41:50.920 --> 41:52.320
Just give me 3,000 yuan.

41:53.110 --> 41:55.880
Mr. Ji, you should not let me take
all the blame for this.

41:55.880 --> 41:57.110
It was an accident.

41:57.110 --> 41:59.840
Besides, so many people are here.

41:59.840 --> 42:00.960
It's so crowded.

42:04.670 --> 42:06.480
It's her. It's her.
